  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with hypertrophic cardiomyopathy are being compared to a control group. IMR will be
      assessed with a pressure wire. Clinical f/u at 3 months and 6 months and a 48 hour holter
      monitor.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
